#originalTopic=It_Would_Be_Much_Safer_If_Everyone_Carried_A_Gun
 Where I live it is illegal to carry a gun unless you are licensed to and our crime rate seems much lower than that of the US. Not as many gangs or killings in ratio to our total population, so wouldn't that show people would be safer if guns were illegal?